==Japanese==

===Adjective===
(まこと)

# roughly translated as [[sincerity]]

===External links===
* [http://www.ajjf.org/article04.html Makoto - Sincerity]

Makoto, normally a Japanese given name used for males, is sometimes used as a first name for females.  In the Japanese language, similar sounds can be represented by very different Kanji.  Whem Makoto is used for a female name it is broken into Ma = honest, sincere and Koto = the japanese 3 stringed tradional harp/guitar.